    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable door dings, faded clear coat on the roof, and a small crack in the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and the driver's seat shows significant bolster wear, though all electronics remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, but it will likely need new brake pads and a suspension tune-up in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that has been used regularly and is priced according to its current state.",
